{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_10", "eventName": "破碎日冕", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "10-11", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "千瘡百孔", "storyInfo": "撤出工廠途中，號角遭遇曼弗雷德。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g8_jail", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說，赫德雷失敗了？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，將軍。我親眼看見了，在剛剛那場戰鬥中，他受了重傷。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才還說了，與他交手的，除了他那名雇傭兵老相識，還有一位薩卡茲女性？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。但她......很善於躲藏，而且她的速度太快。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不敢走太近，我總覺得，她差一點就要發現我了。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明智的選擇。否則的話，你不可能活著回到這裡。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，赦罪師竟然放過了巴別塔的刺客。這是他們的失職，還是他們有意......", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......算了。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷呢，他在哪裡？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還在集結剩餘的雇傭兵，準備繼續去追那些逃走的囚犯。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓他回來吧。那群囚犯的自由會有時限。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......將軍？", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的，他傷得不輕。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍，恕我直言，你為何還這麼信任赫德雷？", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我讓你一直跟著他。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒記錯的話，你並沒有向我提起過，他犯了什麼錯。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可他曾經替巴別塔工作過！", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天就是他手下的雇傭兵壞的事，而且煽動那批雇傭兵的人也是他的老相識，將軍不覺得再這麼重用他，風險實在太大嗎？", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......今天你都看見了。一個維多利亞人是怎麼看另一個維多利亞人的？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要讓一個薩卡茲信任另一個薩卡茲，又有多麼不容易？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們被奪走了一切，被迫習慣了從彼此手上爭奪活下去的權利。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在，我們有了一個新的機會。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你告訴我，你是想回去繼續監視一個可能的薩卡茲間諜，還是隨我一起處理剩下的維多利亞的麻煩們？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍，我們選擇跟著你。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g10_lightinduarea_street_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......呼......我們是不是甩脫他們了？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特先生，我們還不能放鬆警惕。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道......哈......我知道。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......隊長。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你臉上好多血。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血？！老比爾......比爾？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......原來是我自己流的血，那沒什麼要緊的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說老比爾，你倒是喘氣聲重一些啊！我可不想費這麼大力氣背個死人回去。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你......揮扳手的時候輕一點。", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你總是......打到......我腦袋......", "name": "戰士比爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行，今天你說了算。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再堅持一會......我們馬上就要到家了。我沒看錯吧？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#7$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我腦門上淌下來的血有點擋視線......洛洛，你多看著點，我們距離說好的接應點還有多遠？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再走三百多米就到了。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_403_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這守著的是六隊吧？我真的需要他們搭把手了，老比爾，你真是越來越重......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#5$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們有多久沒收到地面隊伍的信號了？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士不是說了，他們要抵達上一個接應點，才會聯繫我們嗎？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我說的就是前一個接應點的自救軍。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照之前的約定，他們每過半個小時就會與我們同步地面上的情況。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟了，我忘了算時間！這過去多久了？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們得上去看一眼。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如前一個接應點已經被薩卡茲發現，那博士他們的隊伍就會有危險。你明明也很擔心摩根和達格達。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我也擔心你！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大不了我去看一眼，維娜，你還是留在這裡，萬一真的有什麼情況，你就趕緊往深處跑......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因陀羅，我不能一直躲在你們身後。最初是老師，然後是你和格拉斯哥幫，還有博士——", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我躲得實在太久了。達格達說的並不是沒有道理。一個總在陰影裡躲躲藏藏的人，會漸漸失去直視太陽的勇氣。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她就是激你！她恨不得你能馬上就帶著她殺進皇宮裡，把那攝什麼王抓出來殺了！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也想立刻回去找格拉斯哥幫。你難道不理解她的想法？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我怎麼可能不懂她。但就是因為我懂，我才......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怕她的衝動最終也會害死她自己。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道不會嗎？她那副德行，我覺得她就是想找死！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你該相信她。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#9$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她會願意為了我們......也為了更多人活下去，即便這意味著極大的痛苦。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#6$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是一名優秀的騎士，也是維多利亞的戰士，她和無數努力活著且仍在為維多利亞奮戰的人一樣。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我......我需要與他們一塊戰鬥。這不是因為我的身份有什麼特殊的，而是因為......我們都是“本地人”。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜......", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得那位指揮官......克洛維希婭女士，她會丟下她的戰士，只為了自己的安全，而往回跑嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟她不熟......但我想她不會。那些戰士很信她。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你覺得我比她差很多嗎？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼可能！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就隨我上去。我們一起確保我們的戰友能順利回家。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g8_jail", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們馬上就能離開這鬼地方了。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“間諜”，你還好嗎？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈......哈......我還好，蔓德拉。", "name": "塔拉密探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近每次聽到有人喊我“間諜”......都是薩卡茲想出了什麼新的刑罰......我都快忘了，這就是我的代號。", "name": "塔拉密探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下回有機會的話，你得選個有品味一些的名字。我看“雄辯家”什麼的就不錯，反正他們都死得渣都不剩下了。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#6"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......", "name": "塔拉密探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先留點力氣吧，領袖還需要你找到的薩卡茲情報。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說......碎片大廈......", "name": "塔拉密探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不要說。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是不想聽，但......我們需要得到領袖的許可。我們的戰士都是很純潔的人，不要給他們造成太大負擔。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我懂......蔓德拉......你一直都是那個好姑娘。", "name": "塔拉密探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......別跟“強盜”一樣油嘴滑舌。煩死了，他們都不在了，害得我一個人在這鬼地方為領袖操心。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好你馬上就要回去了。你不在，那個阿赫茉妮一天到晚佔著領袖身邊的位子，我真怕......真怕......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在怕......什麼？", "name": "塔拉密探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怕領袖和那些貴族走得太近......等哪天她就不要我們了。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領袖她......", "name": "塔拉密探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，我已經確定了其他人的位置，他們還在老地方，替薩卡茲守著門。我們這就去跟他們會合嗎？", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。讓醫療兵準備好，“間諜”長官需要馬上得到治療。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，還有......找個信使，立刻通知城外的莫寧伯爵。我們需要確保“間諜”能儘快見到領袖。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫寧伯爵？你......替領袖拉攏了他？", "name": "塔拉密探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖......在這種時候，我們還是只能指望貴族幫忙......挺可笑的不是嗎？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳......你......你長大了......", "name": "塔拉密探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_421_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你廢話太多了，這不像你，“間諜”。剩下的廢話，等你不是這樣破破爛爛隨時都會死掉的時候再說吧。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#6"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g8_jail", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......停下。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，號角？我們已經看到出口了。", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意你周圍。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三點鐘方向！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.02, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "號角，是薩卡茲！", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.02, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅本，你的彈藥還夠嗎？", "name": "號角"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......哈哈......對不起，號角，其實我還偷偷藏了一枚榴彈。", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直想，等哪天眼看著我又要落到深池或者薩卡茲的手裡......我一定抱著這枚榴彈衝上去。", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......可惜，這榴彈是我們自製的。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那又怎樣......", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，很抱歉，我不想給你這個機會。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？我的榴彈——", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然，自己做的威力就是不太夠。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......可是也不至於......毫髮無傷吧？", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個薩卡茲......", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個薩卡茲就是他們口中的將軍。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......終於見面了。一顆自製榴彈可算不上什麼高規格的招呼。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你見過的維多利亞士兵不會少，薩卡茲。畢竟他們之中的許多人就死在你手上，士兵們的亡靈恐怕排著隊都想擠進你的夢裡。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必妄自菲薄，維多利亞的白狼。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算是放在薩卡茲裡，你也稱得上一名英勇的戰士。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得，在兩百年前的那場戰爭中，讓卡茲戴爾再次化作火海的維多利亞將領裡，就有你的祖先。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是什麼活了幾百年的怪物嗎？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無緣見證那場戰爭。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你說起戰爭時的語氣，和你那些靠吸食別人性命而苟活的同族並沒有什麼差別。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“沾上薩卡茲鮮血的人，必用千倍萬倍的血來償還。”", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當我們是因何而來，維多利亞人？究竟是誰在害怕倫蒂尼姆上空日日夜夜複述著血仇的亡靈？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道嗎？我之所以選擇成為一名職業士兵，就是因為我厭倦了為眼前的戰鬥尋找理由。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來吧，薩卡茲。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留在我耳朵裡的死者的話語並不比你能聽見的少。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且......我答應他們了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在看到我的人活著離開之前，我一定不會倒下。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.02, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}